{"tid":83113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"成日試鞋扮排隊畀錢 店員無嬲仲夾錢送畀佢","createTime":"2017-01-16T13:13:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T05:55:17.000Z","uid":22675,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2c93cf4b082c1f24516ea1b28f7ec9cd4032087c","tid":83113,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:13:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170116/56176636 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170116%2F56176636%20&d=RWxHtKKjDDt9mVk%2FDQYX%2BGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=186d4a56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170116%2F56176636%20&h=79fc3db5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170116/56176636 </a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170115/large/1484472886_3ce3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170115%2Flarge%2F1484472886_3ce3.jpg&h=003edbd5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美國加州28歲男子泰里（Tyree）因為喜歡一雙Nike鞋幾乎每天到運動店，運動店員工眼看他無力支付購買，便夾錢送給他。 <br />\n<br />\n員工奧利娃（Fernando Oliva）指，泰里經常到店內，先周圍看然後要求試同一雙Nike鞋，「10至12次，定期入來說『我可否得到它？我可否試一試？』但他從不真的試鞋，這是有趣的地方」。奧利娃指，泰里每次都會排隊付錢，但就將鞋子留在收銀櫃位，無法付錢。 <br />\n<br />\n奧利娃和一班員工就決定籌錢將鞋送給泰里，待他再來時便讓他試鞋，泰里問他：「多少錢？」奧利娃回應：「160美元（1248港元），但不要擔心，試一試。」 <br />\n<br />\n當奧利娃坦言將鞋給泰里時，他以為對方說笑，顯得十分驚訝。除了Nike鞋外，一班員工亦送上一頂帽、連帽衞衣和運動褲。 <br />\n<br />\n美國廣播公司"},{"pid":"97d202d618d2729c002f6cf73660dd427d7fd009","tid":83113,"uid":37641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:47:58.000Z","msg":"聽日開始去試鞋"},{"pid":"43718ff66e4b49d4e1354d0c034e6d01fea7582c","tid":83113,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:56:14.000Z","msg":"係香港試完唔買既，啲店員會西鳩你面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40c297ee0a56939449f3be51a9dc7b9db3244e5","tid":83113,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T13:57:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係香港試完唔買既，啲店員會西鳩你面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b95c69ed2598e44394308b7939adebef8f46cda","tid":83113,"uid":66779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T14:01:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係香港試完唔買既，啲店員會西鳩你面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但他從不真的試鞋"},{"pid":"2867342c0889b11fce264c024e512163a1c92781","tid":83113,"uid":12370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T14:03:55.000Z","msg":"呢到就算買試耐少少都西你面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf0a5dd312ea4ba057e8c4df050320160697f93","tid":83113,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T14:08:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係香港試完唔買既，啲店員會西鳩你面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但他從不真的試鞋</blockquote><br />\n香港係行入店見你香港人已經西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5c5a0ef3d15c2d6cf3f5c7279259d4909b04eb","tid":83113,"uid":37747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T14:15:55.000Z","msg":"似係夾錢送溫神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803f43a7bedf0f9cddeb43e9a80ded892c208c99","tid":83113,"uid":54930,