 class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直到我走都同佢講聲再見<br />\n當時好想令佢難堪<br />\n<br />\n利申 平時好有禮貌 好憎呢啲爛鬼sales<br />\n而家多數買外國野 一係就搵熟人"},{"pid":"c436ce12495889f9f0f0ce155d7e042ddf0abd72","tid":83113,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:12:49.000Z","msg":"算了<br />\n香港人幸唔到啦<br />\n太貪小便宜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc196848a4e687886403504056084d6d59d72278","tid":83113,"uid":40801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:13:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過試左對鞋兩次<br />\n出過去再番黎 排隊俾錢果陣<br />\n 聽到個員工話我試左好多次<br />\n<br />\n我即刻望過去笑住問佢 你岩先講咩阿<br />\n佢唔敢正視我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直到我走都同佢講聲再見<br />\n當時好想令佢難堪<br />\n<br />\n利申 平時好有禮貌 好憎呢啲爛鬼sales<br />\n而家多數買外國野 一係就搵熟人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2684cf3c6ebe03c4fd937967abe572b86aa3d0f","tid":83113,"uid":24455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:17:20.000Z","msg":"美國一樣有假新聞"},{"pid":"864f94778ed18b6290caac76727238fe22b896ad","tid":83113,"uid":31962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:32:16.000Z","msg":"聽日開始香港成條波鞋街啲人都試鞋唔買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e302c62986fb02fb7b3420d68f308521bb31dc2e","tid":83113,"uid":11420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:33:37.000Z","msg":"店員有discount應該平d 但唔知點解上到新聞"},{"pid":"70ec9330af6782f872efafe4690d9d0757821c12","tid":83113,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:35:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>美國一樣有假新聞</blockquote><br />\n同上次日日去試玩遊戲機一樣"},{"pid":"de1b8ab2b70f4dde6b2be89b7953a5d90d26dd2f","tid":83113,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:37:23.000Z","msg":"香港人同外國人分別<br />\n咁做又有效宣傳<br />\n香港人就見高拜見低踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f629d92474e7d85b28d4a526e78f94c080e1b53","tid":83113,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:37:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>美國一樣有假新聞</blockquote><br />\n同上次日日去試玩遊戲機一樣</blockquote><br />\n呃台灣人咪得囉"},{"pid":"4c59aa6c4ef0d86b38546e67e59c956165f83c2a","tid":83113,"uid":45203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:38:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過試左對鞋兩次<br />\n出過去再番黎 排隊俾錢果陣<br />\n 聽到個員工話我試左好多次<br />\n<br />\n我即刻望過去笑住問佢 你岩先講咩阿<br />\n佢唔敢正視我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直到我走都同佢講聲再見<br />\n當時好想令佢難堪<br />\n<br />\n利申 平時好有禮貌 好憎呢啲爛鬼sales<br />\n而家多數買外國野 一係就搵熟人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母諗起前2日行過collect point<br />\n試左2，3轉衫，企fitting 條女就閪哂口面咁<br />\n叫佢攞新又閪，問野又閪<br />\n我又唔係唔買野鳩試，咁試完唔岩心水就唔要架啦<br />\n又唔係冇禮貌，已經唔該前唔該後笑哂口咁<br />\n到底依家我係sales定你係sales<br />\n正臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n忍住左冇屌佢地，係我冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c806ce5f6b77efac457db211de1ea1af181ac1","tid":83113,"uid":27153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:38:30.000Z","msg":"記得之前有單新聞都類似<br />\n話有個細路冇錢買遊戲機，日日去間鋪到試玩，<br />\n最後啲店員夾錢送咗部機俾佢"},{"pid":"2712ada301adc2c5010defaf4558a842882c5e2f","tid":83113,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:38:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"133f2468c49e6d3a908a0bb0062082d72af7a858","tid":83113,"uid":7186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T16:55:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係請左佢做兼職，俾套制服佢</blockquote><br />\n然後鞋錢係人工度扣返。"},{"pid":"671fd8f1a7c62c5014f34fcd77a6a0946a56e787","tid":83113,"uid":22694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T18:11:50.000Z","msg":"跟之前個bestbuy玩wii段新聞"},{"pid":"480907ca7db95eae32f0a4aad0b3015d84f24821","tid":83113,"uid":60908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T18:15:11.000Z","msg":"如果我唔係真係想買對鞋，都唔敢去試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前買衫都唔會試，一黎煩，二黎驚啲sales閪面，不過近排識咗個fd每次買衫都會試，如果我都咁岩睇中衫都會試埋，其實試下都冇咩呀，啲sales比我想像中好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過去專櫃/稍為貴啲嘅牌子睇野，都好驚啲店員跟住我/睇完唔岩會閪我面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98e4c61280403043a6152f6cc80e4d83e5c2d959","tid":83113,"uid":59639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T18:39:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果我唔係真係想買對鞋，都唔敢去試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前買衫都唔會試，一黎煩，二黎驚啲sales閪面，不過近排識咗個fd每次買衫都會試，如果我都咁岩睇中衫都會試埋，其實試下都冇咩呀，啲sales比我想像中好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過去專櫃/稍為貴啲嘅牌子睇野，都好驚啲店員跟住我/睇完唔岩會閪我面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試野最緊要就係自信 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為d仆街sales會見高拜見低踩 <br />\n最好 fitting room試完出埋黎照鏡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66877c7b724dfbf5cbede17bc84b05f54e5b856f","tid":83113,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T18:43:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試過試左對鞋兩次<br />\n出過去再番黎 排隊俾錢果陣<br />\n 聽到個員工話我試左好多次<