lass=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直到我走都同佢講聲再見<br />\n當時好想令佢難堪<br />\n<br />\n利申 平時好有禮貌 好憎呢啲爛鬼sales<br />\n而家多數買外國野 一係就搵熟人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母諗起前2日行過collect point<br />\n試左2，3轉衫，企fitting 條女就閪哂口面咁<br />\n叫佢攞新又閪，問野又閪<br />\n我又唔係唔買野鳩試，咁試完唔岩心水就唔要架啦<br />\n又唔係冇禮貌，已經唔該前唔該後笑哂口咁<br />\n到底依家我係sales定你係sales<br />\n正臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n忍住左冇屌佢地，係我冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依排減價我都去左買<br />\n旺角朗豪坊對面個間有個啡色長頭髮 空氣瀏海著stain smithb好撚閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 囉前囉後 家下你serve緊我 都唔望你好服務 但連普通做人禮貌都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而同舖其他有d幾好人幾好禮貌"},{"pid":"33378d28e64c143a20d3d57ff54cdb6f16762fc4","tid":83113,"uid":54486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T01:45:03.000Z","msg":"去香檳睇完後樓梯打飛機"},{"pid":"805338c8520ce56ccd28de7927d9f6e1fbefe942","tid":83113,"uid":29947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T01:47:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陣間又有SALES出黎話香港人最垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\npt做過服務業 香港有d客係真係好閪<br />\n但自問出去買野食野唔該前唔該後 總係有d staff你咩都冇做好有禮貌都要閪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依d人就算自己做依行 出去要人serve都係閪客黎"},{"pid":"a3918f4fbeb17768eb12bb99f0c287a4f52ec3f1","tid":83113,"uid":42586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T01:54:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試過試左對鞋兩次<br />\n出過去再番黎 排隊俾錢果陣<br />\n 聽到個員工話我試左好多次<br />\n<br />\n我即刻望過去笑住問佢 你岩先講咩阿<br />\n佢唔敢正視我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直到我走都同佢講聲再見<br />\n當時好想令佢難堪<br />\n<br />\n利申 平時好有禮貌 好憎呢啲爛鬼sales<br />\n而家多數買外國野 一係就搵熟人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母諗起前2日行過collect point<br />\n試左2，3轉衫，企fitting 條女就閪哂口面咁<br />\n叫佢攞新又閪，問野又閪<br />\n我又唔係唔買野鳩試，咁試完唔岩心水就唔要架啦<br />\n又唔係冇禮貌，已經唔該前唔該後笑哂口咁<br />\n到底依家我係sales定你係sales<br />\n正臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n忍住左冇屌佢地，係我冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係架, 香港有班sales仲會話鳩你閪客<br />\n阻住人做生意, 但係又唔諗下<br />\n我嚟得你度買嘢 就要試清楚架啦<br />\n幫客人手試嘢係唔係sales職責所在先?<br />\n係啊嗎, 而家唔係唔好態度 只係要求你provide 一啲service<br />\n如果咁都要黑個客面, 真係好過份<br />\n(以前做過下pt服務業有感而發)"},{"pid":"320be24aac742af3f24f4fb412b4d2406781ac12","tid":83113,"uid":42586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T01:57:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>陣間又有SALES出黎話香港人最垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\npt做過服務業 香港有d客係真係好閪<br />\n但自問出去買野食野唔該前唔該後 總係有d staff你咩都冇做好有禮貌都要閪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依d人就算自己做依行 出去要人serve都係閪客黎</blockquote><br />\n其實係有好多客好閪 但亦都有好多正常客<br />\n如果個sales比上一個閪客玩完<br />\n下一個正常客受番個sales氣 真係講唔通<br />\n做得服務行業就預咗會有仆街<br />\n但都唔該比番啲正常服務比啲正常客<br />\n人地唔係欠咗你(班sales)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43db6ba5e644a06c2edcb25c44d4533eeda308b0","tid":83113,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T01:59:15.000Z","msg":"其實只要大家好禮貌既 大部分都唔會西面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有次去買外套 全個場都係蝗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾個店員塊面西到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都幾有禮貌問件衫有無加大 佢check完之後話無<br />\n我講左句sorry 突然佢唔再西面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲笑笑口話邊堆衫會有加大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我諗好多都係唔鐘意蝗蟲嘈亂巴閉啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ca4bec43ffafbbe268764ae54c1a90c377f5f9","tid":83113,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T01:59:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算了<br />\n香港人幸唔到啦<br />\n太貪小便宜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港人已經比支那壓榨到唔貪小便宜就生存唔到<br />\n樓價物價都比支那狗拉高<br />\n支那狗正仆街"},{"pid":"ae602a7434d13d4e746e97f98ee503afd406ce64","tid":83113,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T01:59:40.000Z","msg":"極邪惡<br />\n隱世小店員工夾錢送波鞋"},{"pid":"d88f35ff03677e79dace1a465794babc461fae9f","tid":83113,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T02:00:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陣間又有[img]SALES<del></del>[/img]支那五毛狗出黎話香港人最垃圾</blockquote>"},{"pid":"eee9f7652bc2f5bb5425dc57ba2f52f40e15d345","tid":83113,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T02:05:22.000Z","msg":"波鞋街班死tb sales 好撚串<br />\n上次試完發覺唔多岩話再睇睇先已經唔該前唔該後，<br />\n之後走個陣細細聲講句：屌 混吉架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"577f10cd244f0c32cb1a6b5a68b998ca480c4448","tid":83113,"uid":29750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T02:43:04.000Z","msg":"marketing <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1bddc5773c089bc6c565045e990058270e90b4","tid":83113,"uid":45170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T03:00:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>波鞋街班死tb sales 好撚串<br />\n上次試完發覺唔多岩話再睇睇先已經唔該前唔該後，<br />\n之後走個陣細細聲講句：屌 混